sentences: Cristiano Giusberti (born December 19, 1970), known by his primary stage name Technoboy, is an Italian hardstyle DJ and producer from Bologna.
Technoboy is a DJ and producer, who started out by playing vinyl in 1992.
He began in 1992 as A&R manager at 'RECORD 66 Music Market for DJs', which he still manages today.
